OL,9,Fdata has showed.
OL,11,FLaura Ruthven Black used to be a carer
OL,12,Fherself, now, she's the one who needs
OL,13,Flooking after.
OL,15,FShe's been waiting for a hip
OL,16,Freplacement for over a year, leaving
OL,17,Fher on crutches; she struggles to walk
OL,18,Fher dog, stand for long periods of
OL,19,Ftime, and even dress herself.
