OL,6,F"It's terrible," she said. "I can't do
OL,7,Fanything. It takes me ages to put my
OL,8,Fown clothes on, I get help sometimes
OL,9,Fputting my socks on, sometimes when
OL,10,FI'm going for a shower."
OL,12,FBut Laura isn't alone, she's just one
OL,13,Fof thousands across currently on a
OL,14,Fwaiting list for a hip or knee
OL,15,Freplacement.
