OL,6,FAccording to data obtained via a
OL,7,FFreedom of Information request, the
OL,8,Fmedian time that a patient who
OL,9,Freceived a new hip from between
OL,10,FNovember 2023 and February 2024 had
OL,11,Fbeen waiting for that operation was
OL,12,F243 days, or around nine months.
OL,14,FKnee replacements took even longer,
OL,15,Fwith a median waiting time of 355
OL,16,Fdays, or just under a year, for
OL,17,Fpatients who received one over the
OL,18,Fsame period.
