OL,6,FThe data also showed that the longest
OL,7,Ftime a patient had waited for a new
OL,8,Fhip, who received one over the three
OL,9,Fmonth period, was 468 days - well over
OL,10,Fa year.
OL,12,FThe waiting time standard for
OL,13,Ftreatment in Scotland is 18 weeks -
OL,14,Fmeaning the typical patient who
OL,15,Freceived a new hip between November
OL,16,Fand February had been waiting almost
OL,17,Fdouble that time standard.
